DISCLAIMER FOR SGK RETIREMENT CALCULATOR:

This calculator is provided for informational purposes only and is based on
MÜKTEZA_01_02_2023.xlsb documentation. While efforts have been made to ensure
accuracy, this tool should not be relied upon as a substitute for official
guidance from the Turkish Social Security Institution (SGK - Sosyal Güvenlik Kurumu).

For official retirement eligibility determination, please contact SGK directly.
SGK official records and guidance take precedence over any calculations made
by this tool.

Usage of this tool does not establish any legal relationship or create any
official documentation with SGK.
